General.Name: Sun Brothers Development Co Ltd
General.Description: Sun Brothers Development Co., Limited engages in the land development and sale business in Taiwan. It also engages in the real estate leasing management; development and construction of industrial and commercial real estate properties, as well as collective housing projects; contract construction of public works; and other businesses. The company was formerly known as Sun Power Development Co., Limited and changed its name to Sun Brothers Development Co., Ltd. in 2013. Sun Brothers Development Co., Limited was founded in 1980 and is based in Taoyuan, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 50, Minquan Road, Taoyuan City, Taiwan, 33846
